1938;;In Old Mexico;;American;;Edward D. Venturini;;William Boyd, Gabby Hayes, Russell Hayden;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/In_Old_Mexico;;Hoppy (William Boyd) and his pals must journey to Mexico after receiving a summons. Upon arrival, they realize that it was fake and that a good friend has been mysteriously murdered. They solve the puzzle with the assistance of the killer's feisty sister and a band of helpful caballeros.[3]